_calculateRewards(uint256).details: Calculate the pending rewards for a specific NFT.

params._tokenId: The ID of the NFT representing the stake.

claimReward(uint256).details: Claim rewards for a specific NFT.

params._tokenId: The ID of the NFT representing the stake.

returns._0: reward The amount of rewards claimed.

collectRevenue().details: Add rewards to the contract and update the reward index.

constructor.details: Constructor initializes the staking token and sets the NFT details.

params._stakingToken: Address of the ERC20 token used for staking.

getStakeInfo(uint256).details: Get the stake details for a specific NFT.

params.tokenId: The ID of the NFT representing the stake.

returns._0: The StakeInfo struct associated with the token ID.

stake(uint256,uint256).details: Stake tokens and lock them for a specified period. Mints an NFT representing the stake.

params.lockPeriod: Lock duration (must match one of the predefined periods).

returns._0: tokenId The ID of the minted NFT.

unstake(uint256).details: Unstake tokens and burn the corresponding NFT. Rewards are claimed automatically.

params.tokenId: The ID of the NFT representing the stake.
